⠀⠘⣿⠀⣿⡇⠀⠈⠀⢀⣘⣿⠋⣽⣿⣿⠻⣶⣄⠈⢧⡀⠀⠀⠁⢀⣿⠀⣴⡿⢋⣿⣸⣶⠉⣷⣬⡀⠀⠀⠀⢿⡟⠀⣴⠁⠀
⠀⠀⠸⡇⠘⠃⠀⠀⠀⠀⡛⢯⣀⠻⠿⢟⣀⣾⠿⠂⠞⢳⡀⠀⠀⣿⣟⠈⠛⠃⣄⣛⣛⣋⣠⠵⢋⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣧⢸⡇⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⣷⠴⡇⠀⠀⣠⠴⠿⣷⣾⣷⣿⣛⣉⠁⠀⠀⠀⢸⡆⠀⠀⠈⠀⠀⠀⠀⠻⢶⣶⣶⡶⠶⠯⠝⠀⠀⠀⢰⠙⣾⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⣧⠀⠑⠀⣸⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠁⠀⢀⣀⠀⣼⡧⠀⠀⠀⠀⣤⣀⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢰⡟⢁⡏⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠻⣆⣀⣴⡏⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣠⣾⠏⠉⠙⠏⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠛⠈⢹⣷⣄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠓⠀⠀⢸⣧⠜⠁⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⠉⢸⣇⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢠⡾⠟⠙⢆⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣠⣼⠛⠛⠷⣄⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣾⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢸⣿⡇⠀⢀⠀⠀⢰⣏⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠛⠳⢦⣀⠀⢀⡴⠛⠋⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠢⡀⠀⠀⠀⣿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢸⢻⡇⠀⢸⡇⠀⠀⠹⢤⣄⣀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠙⠟⠋⠀⠀⠀⣀⡤⠖⠛⠳⠀⠀⠉⣲⠀⢸⠇⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢸⡌⢷⡀⠀⢿⡄⠀⠀⠀⠀⢯⡛⢶⡲⠦⠤⠤⡤⠤⠴⠒⢋⡅⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢠⠏⢠⡟⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠘⣧⠀⠻⣦⡀⠻⣶⡄⠀⠀⠀⠙⠦⣤⣄⣀⣀⣀⣠⡤⠾⠋⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣠⠏⡰⠋⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠙⣧⡀⠈⠻⣦⡈⣿⡄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣠⣾⠷⠋⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⠛⢷⣦⣜⣿⣿⣿⣄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⣤⣾⠟⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠛⠿⢿⣿⣿⣿⣦⣤⣤⣀⣀⣀⣀⣀⣠⣤⣴⣾⡿⠟⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠉⠙⠛⠛⠛⠻⠿⠿⠿⠛⠛⠋⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
EOF
}

############# Main body ############
if [ $1 = "so" ]; then
    afplay $audio_dir/so_audio.mp3 \
    & \
    exit 0
fi

if [ $1 = "so_fluffy" ]; then
    echo ">'so_fluffy!'"
    afplay $audio_dir/so_fluffy_audio.wav \
    & \
    exit 0
fi

if [[ $1 = "fluffy" || $1 = "fluffy!" ]]; then
    afplay $audio_dir/fluffy_short.wav \
    & \
    exit 0
fi

if [[ $1 = "its_so_fluffy" || $1 = "isf" ]]; then
    afplay $audio_dir/its_so_fluffy.mp3 \
    & \
    exit 0
fi

